Turn features into here’s how you will use this.

Screen share if possible. Hit three things:

a) Advanced Audio Suite
Show where their key tracks live (AM, Sleep, maybe a Power track).

Lock in:

For mornings, we’ll use [Track Name]. For sleep, we’ll use [Track Name]. Cool?

b) Vibe Tribe
Show where and how to post, key tags.

