Write it as a sentence together:

Every [weekday / day] at [time], I listen to [Track] in [place], then [action].
b) Daily PM (3–5 min)
Ask and decide:

What’s a realistic evening routine you can hit most nights?
Which track will you play while winding down or falling asleep?
Do you want a 1–10 vibe check or one Journal line?
Sentence:

Before sleep, I play [Track] and do a [vibe check / one‑line Journal].
c) Weekly Rhythm
What’s the minimum weekly touch with Vibe Tribe you can commit to?
Example:

